OL,3,CFormer navy diver needed permanent
OL,4,Ctracheostomy as complication of
OL,5,Cdiabetes
OL,7,FA former Royal Navy diver who needed
OL,8,Flife-changing surgery after a hospital
OL,9,Ffailed to recognise a dangerous
OL,10,Fcomplication of diabetes is calling
OL,11,Ffor lessons to be learned.
OL,13,FGlyn Holgate needed a permanent
OL,14,Ftracheostomy after medics at the Queen
OL,15,FAlexandra Hospital in Portsmouth
OL,16,Ftreated him for gastroenteritis when a
OL,17,Flack of insulin caused a life
OL,18,Fthreatening build up of harmful
OL,19,Fsubstances in his blood.
