OL,7,FDiving was Glyn's job and hobby for 22
OL,8,Fyears. But because of the permanent
OL,9,Fhole in his throat, he can no longer
OL,10,Fdive or swim.JGlyn and his partner say
OL,11,Fthe life changing surgery would not
OL,12,Fhave been necessary if medics hadn't
OL,13,Ftaken so long to diagnose a dangerous
OL,14,Fcomplication of diabetes called DKA
OL,15,Fwhere lack of insulin causes harmful
OL,16,Fsubstances called ketones to build up
OL,17,Fin the blood.
