OL,7,FGlyn says: "I was petrified, I was
OL,8,Fvery scared, yes, I didn't know what
OL,9,Fwas happening, I just knew that I
OL,10,Fwasn't right."JFollowing the surgery
OL,11,Fhe has now lost his lorry driving
OL,12,Flicence, his job in security and his
OL,13,Fdreams of diving holidays in
OL,14,Fretirement.JHe says: "If I'd have had
OL,15,Fthem tests straight away when I went
OL,16,Fin then I would have been treated for
OL,17,FDKA and I would have been out in three
OL,18,Fdays.
