OL,7,F"I wouldn't have been in intensive
OL,8,Fcare, I wouldn't have been in a coma,
OL,9,Fintubated and had a tracheostomy and I
OL,10,Fwould have been living my life as I
OL,11,Falways should have done."JIn a
OL,12,Fstatement Portsmouth Hospitals
OL,13,FUniversity NHS Trust said: "Our teams
OL,14,Fwork hard every day to provide safe,
OL,15,Fcompassionate care to the communities
OL,16,Fwe serve.
OL,18,F"However we know we don't always get
OL,19,Fthis right and apologise that not
OL,20,Fevery patient has the positive
OL,21,Fexperience we want to provide.
